      <title>尼日利亚财富基金的利润在货币，资产收益上飙升了59％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/nigeria-wealth-fund-s-profit-surges-59-on-currency-asset-gains</link>
